sentences.english: Gold and white face has black Arabic numerals.
sentences.chinese: 黃金和白臉黑色阿拉伯語或羅馬數字。

sentences.english: Roman Numeral Converter - Converts integers to roman numeral equivalents.
sentences.chinese: 這個應用程序能將整數轉換爲相當的羅馬數字。

sentences.english: Suppose, for instance, that you wanted to expand the range of the Roman numeral conversion functions.
sentences.chinese: 假設你想要擴展羅馬數字轉換函數的範圍。

sentences.english: Map this number to the Roman numeral system.
sentences.chinese: 將這個數字映射到羅馬數字系統。

sentences.english: The method took a positive integer and turned it into roman numerals .
sentences.chinese: 該方法採取了積極的整數，變成了羅馬數字了。

sentences.english: That ended the practice of tacking on roman numerals to the name "Dream Team."
sentences.chinese: 這也結束了在夢之隊後面加上羅馬數字的習慣。

sentences.english: The same is true for the mapping of Arabic to Roman numerals.
sentences.chinese: 這對於從阿拉伯數字到羅馬數字的映射同樣成立。
